import React from 'react';
import { StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
  
  const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    container: {
        flex: 1,
        backgroundColor: '#000',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
    },

    containerCol: {
        flex: 1,
        flexDirection: 'column',
        backgroundColor: '#000',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
    },

    containerLinha: {
        flex: 1,
        flexDirection: 'row',
        backgroundColor: '#000',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
      },
    containerColumn: {
      
        flexDirection: 'column',
      
      },

    backgroundImage: {
        resizeMode: 'cover',
        flex: 1,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        position: 'absolute',
        width: '100%',
        height: '100%',
    },
    cardContent: {
        flexDirection: 'row',
        marginTop: 5,
        padding: 2,
        marginLeft: 210,
        borderColor: '#FFF',
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.0)', // 40% opaque
        color: 'white',
        fontSize: 16,
        borderRadius: 20
    },


    input: {
        marginTop: 10,
        padding: 10,
        width: 300,
        borderColor: '#FFF',
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)', // 40% opaque
        color: 'white',
        fontSize: 16,
        borderRadius: 10
    },
    texto: {
        marginTop: 2,
        padding: 2,
        width: 300,
        borderColor: '#FFF',
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.0)', // 40% opaque
        color: 'white',
        fontSize: 16,
        borderRadius: 10
    },
    texto2: {
        flexDirection: "row",
        margin: 5,
        padding: 5,
        width: 300,
        borderColor: '#FFF',
        backgroundColor: 'green',
        color: 'white',
        fontSize: 16,
        fontWeight: 'bold'

    },

    texto3: {
        flexDirection: "row",
        margin: 5,
        padding: 5,
        width: 150,
        borderColor: '#FFF',
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.0)', // 40% opaque
        color: 'white',
        fontSize: 16,
        fontWeight: 'bold'

    },
    linha: {
        flexDirection: "row",
        borderColor: '#FFF',
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.0)', // 40% opaque
        color: 'black',
        fontSize: 16,
        fontWeight: 'bold'

    },

    coluna: {
        flexDirection: "column",
        borderColor: '#FFF',
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(152,251,152,0.2)', // 40% opaque
        color: 'black',
        fontSize: 16,
        fontWeight: 'bold'

    },
    
});


export { styles};
